        n: 6,
        t: "Reconstruction and closure",
        d: "Colorectal anastomosis (primary or defunctioning stoma). Retroperitonealise the wound. Place surgical clips at tumor bed to guide adjuvant RT planning. Ensure hemostasis. Close abdomen."
